---
title: Farmer's Market Summer Salmon and Kiwi Relish with BBQ-Spiced Potatoes and Fresh Veggie Jumble
description: Sweet and sassy kiwis are the star of our DIY relish to top succulent salmon. Drizzle lime mayo over top, or serve as a dipper for potatoes! A bounty of fresh veg gives farmers market vibes you won't want to miss.
